title: Global Advantage with Free Trade Zones in China | Catalent in 90 Seconds
description:
Free trade zones offer many advantages for our customers interested in clinical trial supply. The zone provides fast, safe and secure transit to controlled storage situation which can delay or eliminate custom duties. Catalent's Shanhai facility is located in the Waigaoqiao province, the longest running free trade zone in China.

Learn more about how free trade zones work and how Catalent's location can provide a flexible and cost efficient way to supply clinical trials in China and around the globe.
